Description: A comprehensive R package for Traditional Chinese Medicine (TCM)
    network pharmacology research. Enables bidirectional queries of herb,
    compound, and target databases; PubChem-based molecule annotation and
    similarity search; pharmacological network construction with topological
    analysis; herb-based enrichment analysis compatible with GO/KEGG; PPI
    network analysis with 15+ centrality metrics and robustness evaluation;
    machine learning-based biomarker screening (LASSO, Elastic Net, Random
    Forest, SVM-RFE, XGBoost); LLM-powered result interpretation; and
    publication-ready visualizations including Sankey diagrams, docking
    heatmaps, and lollipop plots.
